---

---
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-4">
        We Don't Play Games. We Play To Win.
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Here's what actually separates us from every other agency out there.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Differentiators Grid -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
      <!-- Speed -->
      <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg shadow-xl overflow-hidden">
        <div class="h-1 bg-[#069c4b]"></div>
        <div class="p-8">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="size-8 text-[#069c4b] flex-shrink-0">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M14.615 1.595a.75.75 0 0 1 .359.852L12.982 9.75h7.268a.75.75 0 0 1 .548 1.262l-10.5 11.25a.75.75 0 0 1-1.272-.71l1.992-7.302H3.75a.75.75 0 0 1-.548-1.262l10.5-11.25a.75.75 0 0 1 .913-.143Z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">Speed</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Fast landing page builds using our conversion-focused system. Quick ad setup means you're generating leads in days, not months. No lengthy discovery phases or custom designs that delay results.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Focus -->
      <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg shadow-xl overflow-hidden">
        <div class="h-1 bg-[#069c4b]"></div>
        <div class="p-8">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="text-[#069c4b] flex-shrink-0">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M8 4C5.79086 4 4 5.79086 4 8C4 10.2091 5.79086 12 8 12C10.2091 12 12 10.2091 12 8C12 5.79086 10.2091 4 8 4ZM6 8C6 6.89543 6.89543 6 8 6C9.10457 6 10 6.89543 10 8C10 9.10457 9.10457 10 8 10C6.89543 10 6 9.10457 6 8Z" fill="currentColor"/>
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M8 0C3.58172 0 0 3.58172 0 8C0 12.4183 3.58172 16 8 16C12.4183 16 16 12.4183 16 8C16 3.58172 12.4183 0 8 0ZM2 8C2 4.68629 4.68629 2 8 2C11.3137 2 14 4.68629 14 8C14 11.3137 11.3137 14 8 14C4.68629 14 2 11.3137 2 8Z" fill="currentColor"/>
            </svg>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">Focus</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            We have one goal and do it well. No branding, social media, or email marketing. We build websites and landing pages that convert and then run ads that work. That's it.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Honesty -->
      <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg shadow-xl overflow-hidden">
        <div class="h-1 bg-[#069c4b]"></div>
        <div class="p-8">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="size-8 text-[#069c4b] flex-shrink-0">
              <path d="M10.5 1.875a1.125 1.125 0 0 1 2.25 0v8.219c.517.162 1.02.382 1.5.659V3.375a1.125 1.125 0 0 1 2.25 0v10.937a4.505 4.505 0 0 0-3.25 2.373 8.963 8.963 0 0 1 4-.935A.75.75 0 0 0 18 15v-2.266a3.368 3.368 0 0 1 .988-2.37 1.125 1.125 0 0 1 1.591 1.59 1.118 1.118 0 0 0-.329.79v3.006h-.005a6 6 0 0 1-1.752 4.007l-1.736 1.736a6 6 0 0 1-4.242 1.757H10.5a7.5 7.5 0 0 1-7.5-7.5V6.375a1.125 1.125 0 0 1 2.25 0v5.519c.46-.452.965-.832 1.5-1.141V3.375a1.125 1.125 0 0 1 2.25 0v6.526c.495-.1.997-.151 1.5-.151V1.875Z" />
            </svg>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">Honesty</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            We let you what we can control and what we can't. Your sales team closes dealsâ€”we bring qualified calls. No false promises about closing rates or guarantees we can't keep.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Transparency -->
      <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg shadow-xl overflow-hidden">
        <div class="h-1 bg-[#069c4b]"></div>
        <div class="p-8">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="size-8 text-[#069c4b] flex-shrink-0">
              <path d="M12 15a3 3 0 1 0 0-6 3 3 0 0 0 0 6Z" />
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M1.323 11.447C2.811 6.976 7.028 3.75 12.001 3.75c4.97 0 9.185 3.223 10.675 7.69.12.362.12.752 0 1.113-1.487 4.471-5.705 7.697-10.677 7.697-4.97 0-9.186-3.223-10.675-7.69a1.762 1.762 0 0 1 0-1.113ZM17.25 12a5.25 5.25 0 1 1-10.5 0 5.25 5.25 0 0 1 10.5 0Z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">Transparency</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            You see exactly what you're paying for. Tracked calls, not vanity metrics. Real revenue attribution, not smoke and mirrors. Monthly reports that actually make sense.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>